name: David Benson
description: I am a down-to-earth, caring and sensitive person, looking for someone real. I consider myself to be open and honest, and am not into games. I have a great sense of humor, even a bit devilish at times. My personality can be naughty or nice, but I am always sweet. I feel that it is not what you do; but who you are with that is important. I am easy to talk to and am a great listener. I enjoy romance; long walks/talks, movies, dinner out, travel, weekend getaways, watching sports, and staying in with someone special.
